```plantuml
@startuml OpenIPC_motors

actor "Camera Application" as app
participant "Motors Daemon" as daemon
participant "Driver Wrapper" as wrapper
participant "Kernel Driver" as driver
participant "Hardware" as hw

app -> daemon : Motor Control Request (PTZ/Focus)
daemon -> wrapper : Translate to Hardware Command
wrapper -> driver : Send IOCTL/Device Command
driver -> hw : Execute Low-Level Operation
hw --> driver : Operation Status
driver --> wrapper : Command Result
wrapper --> daemon : Translated Response
daemon --> app : Standardized Response

@enduml
```